<br>
The current window has a title bar, scroll bar and text entry area. The old hitsmode had none of those, which mean that you couldn't accidentally click on the window. Now you can, and it can be really annoying.<br>
<br>
This is a step in the right direction, but it would be nice to be able to set the windows either to have or not have a text entry area. The fact that you can type into your main chat window and direct the text to any other window means that the presence of an entry area is not required.<br>
<br>
